quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,25,"wyqal lahum twbykhana: ma lakum la yansur baedukum bedana?"
  37,26,"bl hum alyawm mnqadwn li'amr allh, la ykhalfwnh wala yhydwn enh, ghyr muntasirin lanfshm"
  37,27,waqbl bed alkufaar ealaa baed yatalawamun wytkhasmwn
  37,28,"qal alatbae llmtbweyn: 'iinakum kuntum tatunana min qibal aldiyn walhq, fthwwinwn ealayna 'amr alshryet, wtunaffirwnna enha, wtzynwn lana aldlal"
  37,29,"qal almtbwewn lltabeyn: ma al'amr kama tzemwn, bal kanat qulubikum munkirat ll'iyman, qabilat lilkufr walesyan"
  37,30,"wma kan lana ealaykum min hujat 'aw qwwat, fnsdkm biha ean al'iyman, bal kuntum -ayha almshrkwn- qwmana taghin mtjawzyn llhq"
  37,31,"flzimana jmyeana waeid rbna, 'iinaa ladhayiqu aledhab, nahn wantm, bima qadamna min dhunubana wmeasyna fi aldnya"
  37,32,"fadllnakm ean sabil allah wal'iiman bh, 'iinaa kunaa daliyn min qblkm, fhlkna; bsbb kfrna, wahlknakm mena"
  37,33,"fa'iin alatbae walmtbweyn mushtarikun yawm alqiamat fi aledhab, kama ashtrku fi aldunya fi mesyt allh"
  37,34,"'ina hkdha nafeal bialadhin akhtaru measy allah fi aldunya ealaa taeth, fndhyqhm aleadhab alalym"
  37,35,"'in 'uwlayik almushrikin kanuu fi aldunya 'iidha qil lhm: la 'ilh 'iilaa allh, wdeu 'ilyha, w'umru bitark ma ynafyha, yastakbirun eanha waealaa man ja' bha"
  37,36,"wyqwlwn: antrk eibadat alihatina laqawl rajul shaeir mjnwn? yenwn rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  37,37,"kdhabu, ma muhamad kama wsfwh bh, bal ja' bialquran waltwhyd, wsddaq almursalin fima akhbru bih eanh min sharae allah wtwhydh"
  37,38,'inkm -ayha almshrkwn- bqwlkm wkfrkm wtkdhybkm ladhayiqu aleadhab al'alim almwje
  37,39,wma tujzawn fi alakhirat 'iilaa bima kuntum temlwnh fi aldunya min almeasy
  37,40,"'ila eibad allah taealaa aladhin akhlsu lah fi ebadth, fakhlshm wakhtshm brhmth; fa'iinahum najwn min aleadhab alalym"
  37,41,awlyk almkhlswn lahum fi aljanat rizq maelum la ynqte
  37,42,"dhlk alrizq fawakih mtnwet, wahum mukramun bkramt allah lahum fi janaat alnaeim aldaym"
  37,43,"dhlk alrizq fawakih mtnwet, wahum mukramun bkramt allah lahum fi janaat alnaeim aldaym"
  37,44,wmn kramthm eind rabihim w'ikram baeduhum bedana 'anahum ealaa surur mutaqabilin fima bynhm
  37,45,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,46,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,47,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,48,"wendhm fi mjalshm nisa' efyfat, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyr 'azwajahuna hisan alaeyn, ka'anahuna bayd mswn lm tmsh alaydy"
  37,49,"waeindahum fi mjalshm nisa' efyfat, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyr 'azwajahuna hisan alaeyn, ka'anahuna bayd mswn lm tmsh alaydy"
  37,50,"faqbl bedhm ealaa bed yatasa'alun ean ahwalhm fi aldunya wama kanuu yueanun fyha, wama 'aneam allah bih ealayhim fi aljnt, whdha min tamam alans"
  37,51,"qal qayil min 'ahl aljnt: laqad kan li fi aldunya sahib mulazim ly"